List.Description:
We've paired a Cabernet and Merlot from Beaulieu Vineyards, one of the most popular wineries in America, with a bountiful selection of savory and sweet edibles. Enjoy these two flavorful, full-bodied wines with jack cheese, crackers, mustard, and much more.

Wine Gift Basket Includes:

  • BV Century Cellars Cabernet Sauvignon:
    This Cabernet Sauvignon offers aromas and flavors of fresh-picked blackberries and spring cherries, hemmed by vanilla and toast.

  • BV Century Cellars Merlot:
    Smooth and supple, with bright acidity and refined tannins, this Merlot shows raspberries and ripe cherry flavors met by a sweet oak finish.

  • Beef Summer Sausage 5 oz
  • Napa Valley Mustard 1.75 oz

  • Caramel Popcorn 3 oz

Pursuant to state laws in New York, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.

List.Name: California Wine Tour Wine Gift Basket
List.Description:
Celebrate California wine country lifestyle with three delicious wines – Pinot Noir, Chardonnay and Merlot – and an assortment of gourmet foods. Arrives in a beautiful basket tied up with ribbon!

Wine Gift Basket Includes:

  • DeLoach Heritage Reserve Pinot Noir:
    This is a balanced pinot noir with a lengthy finish. Red fruit mingles with hints of black pepper on the palate and a round mouthfeel is accented by smooth tannins and a nice acidity. Aromas include cherry, cola, and eucalyptus.

  • Clos LaChance Monterey County Chardonnay:
    This Chardonnay is aged without oak, showcasing the tropical fruit flavors of the grape. Aromas include pineapple, bananas, lemons and a hint of coconut .

  • Wente Sandstone Merlot:
    This Merlot exhibits aromas and flavors of black cherry, blackberry and plum with hints of toasted oak. A smooth mouthfeel and inviting tannins lead to a long, fruity finish.

  • Lemon Almond Biscotti 6 oz
  • Sonoma Jacks Garlic & Herb Cheese 4 oz
  • Spanish Manzanilla Olives 2 oz
  • Beef Summer Sausage 5 oz
  • Sweet & Hot Mustard 9.5 oz
  • Nunes Farms Pistachios 8 oz
  • Toasted Sesame Crackers 2 oz
  • Ghirardelli Masterpiece Truffles 4.3 oz

List.Description:
Silver Oak and Twomey Cellars are two of the most prestigious wineries in California. Both have achieved success with two varietals, Cabernet Sauvignon and Merlot, receiving praise from critics and consumers alike. This is sure to impress the most discriminating wine connoisseur.

Wine Gift Includes:

  • Twomey Cellars Napa Valley Merlot:
    A robust, yet elegant wine that balances intense fruit with suppleness. It has a smooth, velvety mouth-feel and a lovely finish of black fruits and violets.

  • Silver Oak Alexander Valley Cabernet Sauvignon
    A rich wine that achieves a beautiful balance of concentration and finesse. It offers a seamless, harmonious progression of fruit, chocolate and black tea tones.
